#ident	"@(#)ihvkit:pdi/hba.guidelines/README	1.2.2.1"

This directory contains a set of guidelines which are highly recommended
reading for any vendor or developer planning to develop, test, and support
storage device drivers.

gen.guidelines:
   A set of general purpose guidelines for developing UnixWare-compatible
   device drivers.

tech.guidelines:
   A set of Do's and Don't's based on information gathered by a number
   of in-house technical experts.
